Notes:
Nodejs - To run javascript outside the browser. We need nodejs 
Nodejs - It is rune environment for javascript.
Nodejs - It is used to write backend coding
Nodejs - database and files system.tim
=================================
Javascript on browser - window,document,(global object is not present)
Javascript on Nodejs - global (window,document is not present)
==============================================
Node software:

https://nodejs.org/en/
LTS - long term support
===========================
cmd:node -v
========================== 
To run reactjs we need node version greater then 14
==================================
hello.js 
